  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chthonian TD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A co-op action roguelite x tower defense game for <strong>1–4 players</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend against escalating waves.<br>Descend into a crystal mine to grow stronger.<br>Face a powerful enemy that shifts the pace of the run.<br>If you survive - push into <strong>optional Endless Mode</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short runs. Constant pressure. No autopilot.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/b71f04fa1c5397092389d0885f90e750.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/b71f04fa1c5397092389d0885f90e750.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/b71f04fa1c5397092389d0885f90e750.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You’re Always in the Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not passive tower defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You move, aim, dodge, revive teammates and react under pressure while your defenses buy you time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Towers strengthen your defense - player decisions still drive the run.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every Run Evolves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level-ups offer upgrade cards that reshape your build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some make you safer.<br>Some reward greed.<br>Some push the run toward instability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your build changes how the game feels.<br>No two runs play the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/294127065d86aae15a09aa24895d43d8.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/294127065d86aae15a09aa24895d43d8.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/294127065d86aae15a09aa24895d43d8.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Power Has a Price</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay above and hold the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or descend into the mine to accelerate your growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining fuels stronger builds - but leaving at the wrong time can cost the run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Greed is always a decision.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a25981131e9f93b2582ec5f168f0f1a0.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a25981131e9f93b2582ec5f168f0f1a0.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a25981131e9f93b2582ec5f168f0f1a0.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Four Roles. One Team.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fighter</strong> - controls space and absorbs pressure<br><strong>Miner</strong> - accelerates economy and scaling<br><strong>Engineer</strong> - stabilizes lanes and strengthens defenses<br><strong>Medic</strong> - prevents collapse when mistakes happen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XP is shared. Builds diverge. Survival is collective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Depths Await</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Abandoned Mine</strong> is only the beginning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive runs to unlock new regions:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten Ruins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frozen Caverns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molten Depths</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each descent brings <strong>new enemies, new pressure, and a different battlefield.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1–4 player online co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~15 minute structured runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two map styles with distinct pacing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four regions to fight through</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A powerful mid-run enemy encounter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional Endless Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card-based progression each run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Persistent upgrades between runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No friendly fire</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vision</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chthonian TD is built around one idea:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relentless action, meaningful choices, and co-op that actually demands teamwork.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight above. Mine below. Survive together.</strong></p>",
