ilds diverge. Survival is collective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/a103876b96da5c708a5e278b4565e07a.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Depths Await</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Abandoned Mine</strong> is only the beginning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive runs to unlock new regions:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten Ruins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frozen Caverns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molten Depths</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each descent brings <strong>new enemies, new pressure, and a different battlefield.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.poster.avif?t=1774205384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.webm?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4048500/extras/8fd6fc5125db93e9e7b67e0c54e4bab0.mp4?t=1774205384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1–4 player onlin